cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL. 

This paper is about improving the accuracy of image classifiers through data augmentation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also describes a search algorithm to find the best policy, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories as well. Additionally, the paper uses a neural network to evaluate the effectiveness of the augmentation policies, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques to describe the augmentation policies, which could also fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
